# User Api

### Register user1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": {
    "email": "user1@example.com",
    "username": "user1",
    "password": "user1"
  }
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.user.token)
%}

### Register user2
