# Profile Api

### Get profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/profiles/user1
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Follow profile
POST http://localhost:8080/api/profiles/user1/follow
Authorization: {{token}}

### Unfollow profile
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/profiles/user1/follow
Authorization: Token {{token}}

