# Article Api

### Feed articles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/feed?
    offset=0&
    limit=100
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Filter articles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?
    tag=&
    author=&
    favorited=&
    offset=0&
    limit=100

### Create article
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "article": {
    "title": "art2",
    "description": "art1",
    "body": "art1",
    "tagList": ["qwer", "asdf"]
  }
}

### Get article
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2

### Update article
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "article": {}
}

### Delete article
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### List comments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2/comments

### Add comment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2/comments
Authorization: Token {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": {
    "body": "qwer"
  }
}

### Delete comment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2/comments/1

### Favorite article
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2/favorite
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Unfavorite article
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/articles/art2/favorite

